    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut the <strong>cucumber</strong> into quarters lengthways, then chop it into bite-sized pieces</p><p>Chop the <strong>tomato<span class=\"text-danger\">[es]</span></strong> finely</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped cucumber</strong> and <strong>tomato</strong> to the bowl with the pomegranate seeds and add the <strong>white wine vinegar</strong>, 1 tsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong> and a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>– this is your<strong> pomegranate salad</strong></p><p>Slice the <strong>green chilli<span class=\"text-danger\">[es]</strong> </span>finely</p>",
