      "instruction": "<p>Grate the <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p><p>Combine the <strong>grated cheese</strong> with the <strong>cornflour</strong> and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> in a pot and mix until the cheese is fully coated</p><p>Add the <strong>curry powder </strong>and<strong> soft cheese</strong> to the pot with 100ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[200ml]</span> <strong>milk </strong>– this is your<strong> rarebit base</strong></p>",
