      "instruction": "<p>Heat the pot with the rarebit base over a medium heat</p><p>Cook for 1-2 min, stirring frequently, or until the cheese has melted and thickened – this is your <strong>curried rarebit sauce</strong></p><p>Set the <strong>curried rarebit</strong> sauce<strong> </strong>aside<strong> </strong>for later</p>",
